{"tid":1022440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Old Man Yes IT】政府推長者進階數碼培訓　學用App、社交媒體","createTime":"2019-02-15T04:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T13:27:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed4c4c17fef3ee475acf33938aad526b90686c4","tid":1022440,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"政府資訊科技總監辦公室今（15日）公布推出全新為期兩年的長者進階數碼培訓計劃，服務對象為具備基本資訊及通訊科技知識的長者。政府已委託11間長者學苑提供相關培訓課程，長者可到相關的長者學苑參加進階培訓課程，學習在日常生活中應用數碼科技，例如使用電子政府服務、流動應用程式及社交媒體。<br />\n<br />\n目前11間長者學苑正制訂培訓課程的具體安排，料於今年第二季內開始接受報名，而資科辦籌辦的網上學習平台亦將於下半年推出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/295191/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8E%A8%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E9%80%B2%E9%9A%8E%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E5%9F%B9%E8%A8%93-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%A8app-%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94-11%E9%96%93%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%AD%B8%E8%8B%91%E9%96%8B%E7%8F%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F295191%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258E%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2580%25B2%25E9%259A%258E%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E5%259F%25B9%25E8%25A8%2593-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%25A8app-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594-11%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%258B%2591%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%258F%25AD&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=a5ca5cd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/295191/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8E%A8%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E9%80%B2%E9%9A%8E%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E5%9F%B9%E8%A8%93-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%A8app-%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94-11%E9%96%93%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%AD%B8%E8%8B%91%E9%96%8B%E7%8F%AD</a>"},{"pid":"6b857cc3b537ee629a9c5a8de28b9abd5fb89e06","tid":1022440,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=